[The City of Olongapo is a highly urbanized city located in the province of Zambales, Philippines. Classified as a highly urbanized city, it has a population of 221 178 people according to the 2010 census. Along with the town of Subic, it comprises Metro Olongapo, one of the 12 metropolitan areas in the Philippines. - Mod.CP

